com.smartitengineering.version.impl.jgit
Enum SearchProperties

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<SearchProperties>
      com.smartitengineering.version.impl.jgit.SearchProperties
All Implemented Interfaces:
SearchParam, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SearchProperties>
public enum SearchProperties
extends java.lang.Enum<SearchProperties>
implements SearchParam

Represents enum for property name of a query parameter to be used for querying to the Version API. While using it please pay attention to the types of each property and use them wisely; we would like to mention that we will pass through your query params directly without verifying them.

Author:
imyousuf
